text: Savage Frontier is a 1953 American western film directed by Harry Keller and starring Allan Lane, Dorothy Patrick and Eddy Waller.Drew p.18 The film's sets were designed by the art director Frank Arrigo. ==Cast== * Allan Lane as U.S. Marshal Rocky Lane * Black Jack as Rocky's Stallion * Eddy Waller as Nugget Clark * Bob Steele as Sam Webb * Dorothy Patrick as Elizabeth Webb * Roy Barcroft as William Oakes * Richard Avonde as Cherokee Kid * William Phipps as Johnny Webb * Jimmy Hawkins as Davie * Lane Bradford as Henchman Tulsa Tom * John L. Cason as Henchman Buck Matson * Kenneth MacDonald as Marshal Bradley * William Henry as Deputy Dan Longley * Gerry Flash as Henchman Pete * Ed Cassidy as Townsman * Art Dillard as Henchman * Frank O'Connor as Townsman * Jack O'Shea as Townsman * Lee Shumway as Doc Pearson * Tom Steele as Henchman ==References== ==Bibliography== * Bernard A. Drew. Motion Picture Series and Sequels: A Reference Guide.
